WITH SupplierPartDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_name AS supplier_name,
        p.p_name AS part_name,
        SUBSTRING(p.p_comment FROM 1 FOR 20) AS short_comment,
        CONCAT('Region: ', r.r_name, ', Nation: ', n.n_name) AS location_info,
        SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_qty
    FROM 
        supplier s
    JOIN 
        partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    JOIN 
        part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
    JOIN 
        nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
    JOIN 
        region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
    GROUP BY 
        s.s_name, p.p_name, p.p_comment, r.r_name, n.n_name
)
SELECT 
    supplier_name, 
    part_name, 
    short_comment, 
    location_info,
    total_available_qty
FROM 
    SupplierPartDetails
WHERE 
    total_available_qty > 50
ORDER BY 
    location_info, part_name

SELECT COALESCE("SUPPLIER_NAME", "SUPPLIER_NAME") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "PART_NAME", "SHORT_COMMENT", "LOCATION_INFO", "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QTY"
FROM (SELECT ANY_VALUE("supplier"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", ANY_VALUE("part"."p_name") AS "PART_NAME", ANY_VALUE(SUBSTRING("part"."p_comment", 1, 20)) AS "SHORT_COMMENT", ANY_VALUE(CONCAT('Region: ', "region"."r_name", ', Nation: ', "nation"."n_name")) AS "LOCATION_INFO", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QTY"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "part" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "region" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_name", "part"."p_name", "part"."p_comment", "region"."r_name", "nation"."n_name") AS "t1"
WHERE "t1"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QTY" > 50
